        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 4. Comparison of head scalation in lateral view of the type specimens of Pareas monticola complex members: a: Pareas monticola holotype (BM(NH) 1946.1.20.5, adult male); b: Pareas victorianus sp. nov. holotype (CAS 224415, adult male); c: Pareas sp. from Kachin State (CAS 235254, adult female). Drawings by L.B. Salamakha." ;
